<h2>Introduction: Why Choose Extreme Ghost Hunting</h2>
<p>You’re not looking for a museum exhibit or a tame historical tour — you want pulse-quickening stories, hands-on participation, and an experience that gets talked about back at the bar. Extreme ghost hunting adventures deliver that: guided ghost tours, overnight paranormal hunts, and app-enhanced realities that mix storytelling with technical gear.</p>
<p>These activities fold history, local lore, and a little theatricality into something you can touch: a tour guide who knows every creak, an investigator who teaches you how to use a meter, or a midnight cruise where the sea and the stories clash. You’ll get practical things to expect, safety advice, and tips that make these tours accessible and fun.</p>
<h2>How to Use This Guide</h2>
<p>Think of this as a companion for choosing the right paranormal activity for your travel style. Each section covers the experience, what you’ll actually do, time and cost expectations, safety and accessibility notes, and pro tips to get the best night possible.</p>
<p>You’ll find checklists and comparisons so you can quickly decide whether to book a haunted walk, a bus tour, an overnight hunt, or a VR/AR experience. By the end you’ll feel ready to book confidently and responsibly.</p>
